Depends: qt6-base (>= 6.4), qt6-wayland, libraw19 (>= 0.20), libtiff6 (>= 4.3), ${misc:Depends}
Description: Fujifilm S3 Pro RAF to DNG converter
 A desktop application for converting Fujifilm FinePix S3 Pro .RAF files
 into editable DNG files, with a focus on the Super CCD SR II sensor's
 separate S and R responses.
 .
 The application loads Fujifilm S3 Pro RAF files, extracts separate S and R
 shot data, merges both responses into a highlight-safe 6MP CFA DNG, and
 preserves the original embedded RAF preview for the GUI file list and DNG
 preview embedding.
